USAGE: @G{shield} agents [OPTIONS]

  List SHIELD Agents.

  Agents perform all backup / restore / purge / test operations on
  behalf of the SHIELD Core.

@B{Options:}

  By default, all registered agentswill be displayed.
  You may filter the results with the following command-line flags.

  --visible       Only show agents that are available to tenants
                  to configure storage and data systems.

  --hidden        Only show agents that are NOT available to
                  tenants to configure storage and data systems.

  -l, --limit     Only show the given number of agents.

@B{Examples:}

  # What Agents can people use?
  @W{shield agents} @Y{--visible}

